combtxt:THIS FORM IS BEING UPDATED 5/29/12.  TRAIN 155 EAST WAS SLOWING FOR ITS MARTHA STATION STOP WHEN A D UMP TRUCK BACKED IN FRONT OF THE TRAIN AT A CONSTRUCTION CROSSING.  TRAIN WAS SOUNDING BELL AND HORN .  TRAIN STRUCK THE DUMP TRUCK KNOCKING IT OFF THE TRACKS.  TRAIN CAME TO A STOP AND DID NOT DERAIL.   THERE WERE NO INJURIES TO THE DRIVER OR CREW.  THERE WERE NO PASSENGERS ON THE TRAIN. :inci
